  "detailed_description": "A cute, joyful, and casual light adventure, welcome to <strong>Kagura's Dreamland</strong>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fantasy World of a High School Girl</h2>Kagura's Dreamland contains 16 adventure levels plus 3 special levels, totaling 19 maps with different features for players to explore. On the way, players will go through forests, deserts, snowfields, gorges, etc., encounter different monsters, learn new skills, and defeat the ultimate enemy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can collect crystals on the map and trade them for more powerful weapons to face more dangerous challenges. In addition, after rounds of battle, Kagura's level will increase, allowing her to perform more powerful attacks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unbearably cute little creatures!</h2>These little bears and kittens are so cute that it's a shame you have to fight them in your dreams. But don't worry, no little creatures are harmed in these dreams.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Refreshing Music</h2>Each level is accompanied by relaxing music, which is different from the tense action games, and Kagura is only enjoyable along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farm in Wonderland</h2>The pets of Kagura have been lost in the dream world, traverse various levels and bring them back to the farm in wonderland.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A cute, joyful, and casual light adventure, welcome to <strong>Kagura's Dreamland</strong>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/4bb626179562592a1795394d97a08211.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fantasy World of a High School Girl</h2>Kagura's Dreamland contains 16 adventure levels plus 3 special levels, totaling 19 maps with different features for players to explore. On the way, players will go through forests, deserts, snowfields, gorges, etc., encounter different monsters, learn new skills, and defeat the ultimate enemy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f6f50cf78a69169b2b9f9e2aa009e7e1.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can collect crystals on the map and trade them for more powerful weapons to face more dangerous challenges. In addition, after rounds of battle, Kagura's level will increase, allowing her to perform more powerful attacks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unbearably cute little creatures!</h2>These little bears and kittens are so cute that it's a shame you have to fight them in your dreams. But don't worry, no little creatures are harmed in these dreams.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/a5e4198aa03691c6ef46cfa3f0a845f3.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Refreshing Music</h2>Each level is accompanied by relaxing music, which is different from the tense action games, and Kagura is only enjoyable along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/f8abfb358c33af3ab0a985e48d93be1c.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farm in Wonderland</h2>The pets of Kagura have been lost in the dream world, traverse various levels and bring them back to the farm in wonderland.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.poster.avif?t=1694946761\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.webm?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461710/extras/8fcd1b099dd20115f1288f56b8a2e469.mp4?t=1694946761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
